Package: ros-kilted-pointcloud-to-laserscan
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ros-kilted-laser-geometry, ros-kilted-launch, ros-kilted-launch-ros, ros-kilted-message-filters, ros-kilted-rclcpp, ros-kilted-rclcpp-components, ros-kilted-sensor-msgs, ros-kilted-tf2, ros-kilted-tf2-ros, ros-kilted-tf2-sensor-msgs, ros-kilted-ros-workspace
Description: Converts a 3D Point Cloud into a 2D laser scan.
 This is useful for making devices like the Kinect appear like a laser scanner for 2D-based algorithms (e.g. laser-based SLAM).
